                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-06-30">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 30, 1896</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Inquire and report when decision appellate tribunal <hi rend="italic"
                        >Competitor</hi> case is expected.</p>
